pos_mean_info_list.mean: 可信的；声誉好的；值得称赞的
信任；凭证；祭器台（等于credence table，credenza）

bilingual.source: You’ll also need to cite references to gain credibility.
bilingual.target: 你也需要引用参考来获得信息的可靠性。

bilingual.source: The system has good real-time capability and high credibility.
bilingual.target: 该系统经实践验证，实时性强、可靠性高。

bilingual.source: The paper researches the credibility of the financial statements analysis in seven aspects.
bilingual.target: 本论文从七个方面对报表分析的可靠性进行了探索性研究.

bilingual.source: Bitcoin has seen rapid growth this past year, which in turn has increased the coin's credibility as an investment.
bilingual.target: 比特币价格在过去一年里急剧增长，这样反过来也增加了它的投资可靠性。

bilingual.source: However, the credibility of the ETH as an explanation for abductions is disputed by most psychologists who have investigated this phenomenon.
bilingual.target: 但是，外星人假说来解释绑架事件的可靠性在那些调查过这些现象的心理学家中存在争论。

bilingual.source: It discusses the design of power-fail protection circuit for SCM from hardware and software, and analyzes the credibility of power-fail protection in detail.
bilingual.target: 详细地介绍了单片机樟电保护电路的设计原理及硬、软件实现方法，分析了其可靠性。

bilingual.source: The methods of the rationality test of measuring-data in the brine were introduced in order to guaranty the credibility and accuracy of measuring-data in laboratory.
bilingual.target: 介绍了卤水试验监测数据的合理性的几种检验方法，以保证实验室监测数据的准确性与可靠性。

bilingual.source: To complete a regional network to provide navigation services with high precision and credibility, China will launch more satellites within the coming two years.
bilingual.target: 为了完成北斗区域卫星导航系统建设提供的高精确度和高可靠性导航服务，中国将在未来两年里发射更多的卫星。

bilingual.source: It showed that it was of better credibility to analyze the genetic diversity and relative relationship by using microsatellite and AFLP fingerprinting.
bilingual.target: 这表明同时应用微卫星和AFLP指纹分析我国地方鸡种的遗传多态性和品种间的亲缘关系，其结果具有更高的可靠性和科学性。

bilingual.source: Since the proposed line states model is complete and consistent with actual operating conditions, the results of system reliability analysis based on this model are more accuracy and credibility.
bilingual.target: 所建线路状态模型完整，符合实际的运行状况，从而使得基于所提模型得到的系统可靠性分析结果的准确性及可信性更高。

yingyinNormal.en: We will destroy Garrett Walker's credibility and the case will fall apart. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要让加勒特·沃克名誉扫地，这事便会不攻自破。行。

yingyinNormal.en: The food didn't matter. Once it got out there were rats in the kitchen, oh, man, the restaurant was closed and Ego lost his job and his credibility.
yingyinNormal.zh: 食物好坏并不重要，但厨房发现老鼠，餐厅就得关门，伊古也因此失去他评论美食的工作。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 可靠性；信用；可信性

word_family.mean: adj. 可信的；令人信服的；能使人相信某事会发生（或成功）的

examination_example.sentence: Think about what the powerful person cares about—it may be the <highlight>credibility</highlight> of their team or getting a project done on time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 想想有权势的人关心什么——可能是他们团队的可信度，或者是按时完成一个项目。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Credibility</highlight> "happens" to a discovery claim — a process that corresponds to what philosopher Annette Baier has described as the commons of the mind.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一项发现主张拥有可信度——这个过程同哲学家安妮特·拜尔所描述的“思想的一致性”相符。

examination_example.sentence: This is the <highlight>credibility</highlight> process, through which the individual researcher's me, here, now becomes the community's anyone, anywhere, anytime.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是可信性过程，通过这个过程，在这里，个体研究者的“我”现在变成了社区中的“任何人”、“任何地点”以及“任何时间”。
